      "text": " [https://umap.openstreetmap.fr/ja/map/historical-recordings-map_1414227 Historical Recordings Map - uMap - Online map creator]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1783133860,
      "updated": 1783133864
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4876ab0000000000d8f81f",
      "text": " \t自作のSPレコードの地図に台湾の主だった蒐集家を追加",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1783133868,
      "updated": 1783133895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a48cf8f0000000000b87e19",
      "text": " \t\t他前から入れようと思っていた諸々を追加",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1783156624,
      "updated": 1783156637
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4876ca0000000000d8f820",
