      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1783133899,
      "updated": 1783133922
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4876e20000000000d8f821",
      "text": " \t\t大陸産も含め世界で最も貴重な[中国語SPレコード]のコレクションを持っているらしい",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1783133922,
      "updated": 1783159605
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4877120000000000d8f823",
      "text": " \t\t\tついでにこれに関するすごい文量の論文も仕上げたとか",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1783133971,
      "updated": 1783134001
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4876f70000000000d8f822",
      "text": " \t\t[https://www.scmp.com/magazines/post-magazine/long-reads/article/3222718/sun-yat-sen-shanghai-jazz-tears-fears-bakelite-shellac-and-78s-record-collection-ages From Sun Yat-sen via Shanghai jazz to Tears for Fears, on Bakelite, shellac and 78s, a record collection for the ages | South China Morning Post]",
