      "updated": 1783142245
    },
    {
      "id": "6a48992300000000007294bf",
      "text": " 3DCADとは少し違うが[Blender]は無料でうまいこと業界に取り込まれてる感がある",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783142691,
      "updated": 1783143884
    },
    {
      "id": "6a489dcb00000000004d9697",
      "text": "  趣味で使ってるだけなので仕事面でどうかはよく知らない",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783143884,
      "updated": 1783143895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a489f9600000000004d9698",
      "text": "  [Maya]とか[Shade]とかは今どうなってるんだろう？",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783144345,
      "updated": 1783144393
    },
    {
      "id": "6a48a5d5000000000047f1c0",
      "text": " [gimp]は[Photoshop]の代替には足りなそう",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783145941,
      "updated": 1783145981
    },
    {
      "id": "6a48cf540000000000b87e17",
      "text": " \t一応[Photoshop]風のUIにしたフォークがあります[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1783156564,
      "updated": 1783156578
    },
    {
      "id": "6a48cf620000000000b87e18",
      "text": " \t\t[https://github.com/Diolinux/PhotoGIMP GitHub - Diolinux/PhotoGIMP: A Patch for GIMP 3+ for Photoshop Users · GitHub]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1783156579,
      "updated": 1783156579
    },
    {
      "id": "6a48a5fe000000000047f1c1",
      "text": " [Illustrator]はまだ無料の代替が無さそう",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1783145983,
      "updated": 1783146010
    },
    {
      "id": "6a48a61a000000000047f1c2",
      "text": "  [Inkscape]はちょっと違うかな？",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
